tswitem.name: Signet of Houdini's Guile
tswitem.tooltip:
Signet of Houdini's Guile
Signet (QL 10)
Tradeable
Effect: Whenever you are Impaired or Hindered, the currently running recharge timers on your crowd control breaking abilities are reduced by 3/6/9 seconds. This Signet can be attached to Head Talismans.
